/remember
- to use past mails and summaries in context
- default will be /remember[TE,2D]
- eg /remember[XE,4W,10D,2M,2Q] -- to keep past 4 weeks weekly summaries, past 10 days daily summaries, past 2 months monthly summaries, and past 2 quarters quarterly summaries in context
  where X,
  * -> all retrievable
  T -> todays retrievable
- later relevant topics are added by cosine similarity

/embeds
- to forego use of embeddings to search for similar topics from past memories
- using /nocosine and /remember[] will be like starting a new chat with only system prompt in context

/readobs
- to make use of documents from obsidian vault as context